<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7741fa21-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s408f"><num value="408f">§ 408f.</num><heading> Former Siskiwit Islands Bird Reservation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Siskiwit Islands Bird Reservation is abolished and shall after <date date="1942-03-06">March 6, 1942</date>, be a part of the Isle Royale National Park.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7741fa22-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/act/1942-03-06/ch152/s2">Mar. 6, 1942, ch. 152, § 2</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/56/138">56 Stat. 138</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
